room_title: Escape room "Undercover Alley" by Breakout Games - Nashville in Nashville
review: We had two groups of teens that competed against each other. They had a great time. The staff was amazing!

room_title: Escape room "Undercover Alley" by Breakout Games - Nashville in Nashville
review: We had an awesome time. It was everyone’s first time doing an escape room. The staff was friendly and our game was challenging which our group liked. They gave us a few extra minutes so we could complete the entire game. Can’t wait to go back and experience a different room! Thanks!

room_title: Escape room "Undercover Alley" by Breakout Games - Nashville in Nashville
review: We had so much fun, we did two rooms in a day! (Which I dont really recommend because it is exhausting) The customer service was amazing! Definitely going back for another round!

room_title: Escape room "Undercover Alley" by Breakout Games - Nashville in Nashville
review: We were first and second-time escape room participants. Lily was our coordinator and she did a phenomenal job! Gave amazing hints and didn't make us feel bad for asking for one haha. We will definitely go back for our next game.

room_title: Escape room "Undercover Alley" by Breakout Games - Nashville in Nashville
review: GREAT GAME with a GREAT GUIDE named GABE! Our group had a very challenging room but found clues with occasional help from Gabe who was our 'calming clue master'. Loved the experience!
